column5: I have a new Lowrence X 52 fish finder c/w transducer never been used (came with the boat) I will sell it for $150.00 (before someone PMs me and tells me to put it in the clasifieds, I will but @ $175.00 which is still a good deal) Just wanted to give OFNr's first crack and a special deal.
A solid unit at a great price. Thanks for posting, Cliff.
dang makes me want to go buy another boat just so I can get it Cliff. Thanks for the offer.   Art
